page.title: 13A day in my life (continued)
page.content: we did some English and when that was over it was 12:00pm and that means lunch.At about 12:20pm we had another playtime until 1:00pm and after that it was drama.For drama we were doing about when Victoria was on the throne and I was a street urchin.We did drama up to 2:15pm and after that we had another playtime until 2:30pm.After that we did some finishing of project work and then at 3:05pm we went home. When I got home from school i got ready for cubs and then I went to Lockerley for a cub meeting.When i went home from cubs it was 8:15pm and I had my dinner,read a little bit and then went to bed.
